{"tid":2395792,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Times Magazine 公開炫耀有幕後組織操控美國大選?","createTime":"2021-02-05T06:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T20:08:10.000Z","uid":331821,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"341f7581eed4c89b6a35c570ded405f80fd0df0c","tid":2395792,"uid":331821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:23:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://time.com/5936036/secret-2020-election-campaign/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F5936036%2Fsecret-2020-election-campaign%2F&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9Eb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=6849818d\" target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/5936036/secret-2020-election-campaign/</a><br />\n<br />\nThat&rsquo;s why the participants want the secret history of the 2020 election told, even though it sounds like a paranoid fever dream&ndash;<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">a well-funded cabal of powerful people, ranging across industries and ideologies, working together behind the scenes to influence perceptions, change rules and laws, steer media coverage and control the flow of information</span></span></strong>. They were not rigging the election; they were fortifying it. And they believe the public needs to understand the system&rsquo;s fragility in order to ensure that democracy in America endures."},{"pid":"b12bfbbf463592da7f10608353165bb433f7ecac","tid":2395792,"uid":47080,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:28:45.000Z","msg":"全世界都知，得左膠唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44729ccfd7fe9521ff0faff3548d1d769df9dfa","tid":2395792,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b12bfbbf463592da7f10608353165bb433f7ecac","tid":2395792,"uid":47080,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:28:45.000Z","msg":"全世界都知，得左膠唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:30:08.000Z","msg":"左膠一定知"},{"pid":"a34f383f81f53700744189095f61ecb9d6407593","tid":2395792,"uid":258345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:31:47.000Z","msg":"tldr<br />\n<br />\n但最後係話人民既意願先係主力咁<br />\n<br />\n點都好，好期待拜登除左講一堆好聽既rhetoric，同係咁簽行政命令之外仲可以為世的做到咩野"},{"pid":"4e28a1a4d0af21915c3003edf7d61a5f498fe200","tid":2395792,"uid":331821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:47:51.000Z","msg":"Their work touched every aspect of the election. <span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">They got states to change voting systems and laws</span></strong></span> and helped secure hundreds of millions in public and private funding. They fended off voter-suppression lawsuits<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"large\">, recruited armies of poll workers </span></strong></span>and got millions of people to vote by mail for the first time. They successfully <span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>pressured social media companies</strong></span></span> to take a harder line against disinformation and used data-driven strategies to fight viral smears."},{"pid":"d4d7a7361593c7925fb8f28153e60b40ac2c0f3c","tid":2395792,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf04378d50676423d10c92db6f0270d3bfbf888","tid":2395792,"uid":64191,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a34f383f81f53700744189095f61ecb9d6407593","tid":2395792,"uid":258345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:31:47.000Z","msg":"tldr<br />\n<br />\n但最後係話人民既意願先係主力咁<br />\n<br />\n點都好，好期待拜登除左講一堆好聽既rhetoric，同係咁簽行政命令之外仲可以為世的做到咩野"},"citedBy":0,"r